LOCUS       tRNA-gRNA_position_[D1_2]_(GB1205) 3220 bp    DNA     circular SYN 15-DEC-2025
DEFINITION  tRNA and scaffold for the assembly of GBoligomers for the first
            position (positon [D1_2]) of a polycistronic tRNA-gRNA regulated by
            the dicot U6-26 or U6-1 promoter (3-part multiplexing).
